      <p>By attending an event you agree that you do so at your own risk,
      are voluntarily participating, assume all risk of injury to yourself,
      and release and discharge AACO and its staff from any and all claims
      or causes of action, known or unknown, arising out of AACO's
      negligence.</p>
    <div>
  </div>
{% endblock main_content %}
